Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.85,0:00:08.48,Default,Ara,0,0,0,,Aku sudah berhenti bermain karuta.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.26,0:00:12.36,Default,Chi,0,0,0,,Cepat!
