Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.02,0:00:23.52,Default,Chi,0,0,0,,Mau bagaimana lagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.52,0:00:25.71,Default,Chi,0,0,0,,Aku tak bisa tidur semalam.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.71,0:00:28.67,Default,Tai,0,0,0,,Ya ampun, seperti anak kecil saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.33,0:00:30.60,Default,Tai,0,0,0,,Kau berutang jus padaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.60,0:00:31.99,Default,Chi,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.43,0:00:34.49,Default,Chi,0,0,0,,Ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.49,0:00:35.93,Default,Chi,0,0,0,,Aku beli ini dan manju.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.15,0:00:36.96,Default,Tai,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.96,0:00:39.03,Default,Tai,0,0,0,,Kalau itu aku sudah membelinya.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.18,0:00:41.81,Default,Chi,0,0,0,,Aku akan makan ini.
